summary: A RaceMenu preset for my character. Enjoy!
descriptionHtml:
A RaceMenu preset of my character. Feel free to use it as a base for your character or use it as is for your own playthroughs.
[u] [/u]
[u] REQUIREMENTS[/u]

RaceMenu and all of its prerequisites. -[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624] http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624

[/url] Apachii Sky Hair and "..............................." - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168
[/url]
[b][u]TO GET IT TO LOOK LIKE THE SCREENSHOTS[/u][/b]

CBBE and "........................"  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/

[/url] XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended and "..................." -[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68000] http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68000[/url]

Armour used in Screenshots: The Lily by pottoply - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71843]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71843[/url]
[u]
INSTALLATION[/u]

Download manually, [u]NOT WITH NMM[/u], and place in the folder [Skyrim > Data > SKSE > Plugins > CharGen > Presets] If the folders from SKSE onwards don't exist, create them. Place the file in there. 
In-game, open up the RaceMenu and select the Presets tab in the top-right corner. press F5 or "Load Preset" and select "Mari" from the list.
author: MrMeow356
